    {
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "runOnceForEachItem",
        "jsCode": "const retrieval = $('Retrieval Code').item.json;\nconst history = $('Code in JavaScript').item.json.history;\n\n// Build alternating user/assistant history pairs\nconst historyMessages = [];\nhistory.forEach(turn => {\n  if (turn.question) historyMessages.push({ role: 'user', content: turn.question });\n  if (turn.answer) historyMessages.push({ role: 'assistant', content: turn.answer });\n});\n\n// Current question with injected context\nconst currentMessage = {\n  role: 'user',\n  content: `CONTEXT:\\n${retrieval.contextBlock}\\nQUESTION: ${retrieval.question}\\nAnswer based strictly on the context above.`\n};\n\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    ...retrieval,\n    messages: [...historyMessages, currentMessage],\n    fullPrompt: [...historyMessages, currentMessage]\n      .map(m => `${m.role.toUpperCase()}: ${m.content}`)\n      .join('\\n\\n')\n  }\n};\n```\n\nClick **Close**.\n\n---\n\n## Step 4: Update the Basic LLM Chain Node\n\nOpen the **Basic LLM Chain** node and update the **Prompt field** to:\n```\n{{ $json.fullPrompt }}"
      },
